      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable commuter for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the trim pieces. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. It has been regularly serviced, and while it isn't a show car, it runs reliably and is ready for its next owner.",
