      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I've babied this car since day one, so it's spotless inside and out. No dings, no scratches, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so feel free to reach out and come take a look. You won't be disappointed!",
