    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a benchmark for the S54-powered chassis, maintained to an exacting standard. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a high-pressure dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band to the 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This example features a pristine factory subframe with proactive reinforcement, Bilstein PSS10 coilover suspension for sharpened turn-in, and freshly shimmed valves. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible paint correction required. A true collector-grade specimen with zero mechanical deficiencies.",
