    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence: a 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in a stunning GT Silver Metallic finish. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of wear. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the black leather interior still carries that new-car scent; the bolsters are firm, the stitching is immaculate, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. With incredibly low mileage and a documented pedigree, this car offers a showroom-fresh experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. It drives as tightly and smoothly as the day it rolled off the assembly line, providing an unfiltered connection to the road.",
